Keep an eye on those expiration dates.
I've been burned more than once.

133
00:07:17,719 --> 00:07:19,994
I'm not gonna get involved
in your relationship.

134
00:07:20,159 --> 00:07:22,798
Come on. It's just a simple favor.
When's the last time...

135
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:25,309
-...| asked you to do something for me?
-Yesterday.

136
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:29,029
You made me look in your ear
to see if there was a ladybug in it.

137
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:32,391
Last time I asked you to do something
that wasn't a medical emergency?

138
00:07:32,599 --> 00:07:36,672
Yesterday. You made me look in your ear
to see if there was a ladybug in it.

139
