I could have this experience and enjoy it.

149
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:14,236
Thank you. That means a lot to me.

150
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:16,993
Oh, don't thank me.
Thank wireless technology.

151
00:08:17,159 --> 00:08:20,071
Yeah, I realized I can go
to your aunt's awful party...

152
00:08:20,239 --> 00:08:24,152
...and still spend the whole day
gaming with my friends.

153
