195
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:49,515
[LEONARD AND RAJESH LAUGHING]

196
00:10:49,999 --> 00:10:53,036
-l was wrong. It's still funny.
-Oh, good.

197
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:55,119
[CACKLES]

198
00:10:59,399 --> 00:11:00,514
Oh.

199
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:03,797
-Amy, what's wrong?
-My boyfriend's ajerk.

200
00:11:04,959 --> 00:11:07,553
Well, I know he didn't cheat on you,
so, what happened?

201
00:11:09,759 --> 00:11:11,590
I had to go to my aunt's party by myself.

202
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:15,070
